{"tid":2064586,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"信報：支共想國安法設‘最低刑期’及唔設陪審團；咁解釋咗點解大波嬅話唔跟普通法","createTime":"2020-06-15T02:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T03:02:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dbe6f59ff7c4bb3e53dcc22289df9c215cc67850","tid":2064586,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯有身處建制陣營的法律界人士分析，現行普通法制度下並沒有「最低刑期」，估計他們所建議的是「量刑指引」。他解釋，此做法並非新事物，目前販運不同種類及數量的毒品，法庭都有量刑指引參考，例如藏有多少克冰毒最低要判監N年等。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該法律界人士憂慮，顛覆國家、分裂國家等罪行很難量化，若定罪設有「最低刑期」，在普通法下恐怕難以執行。<br />\n<br />\n設陪審團否意見紛紜<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，除了罰則刑期，部分人大政協另一關注點是審理「香港國安法」案件時應否設陪審團，這方面的意見紛紜，作風較「鷹派」的港區代表反對有陪審團，甚至提出另設特別法庭審訊，理由是涉及國家安全的案件，不宜交陪審團「定生死」⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2493745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2493745&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8gaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=33868bf3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2493745</a>"},{"pid":"9344dfc0b91639b2ec2135d80bec0aff0d755e8f","tid":2064586,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:26:54.000Z","msg":"另外：<br />\n自由黨可能派梁日昌同大口狗爭位<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2494183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2494183&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8gaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=364f03d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2494183</a>"},{"pid":"383cb4cf9c15fcf5a4a042da1f3e550d136cf19b","tid":2064586,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"直接送中算啦，反正都係任你講"},{"pid":"db503667102cc05c4b7a50c6bcee00c3d99f0f68","tid":2064586,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9344dfc0b91639b2ec2135d80bec0aff0d755e8f","tid":2064586,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0